<plot>After falling while jogging in the park, Lewis is helped up by Edgar, a stranger who says he remembers him from high school. Lewis remembers him vaguely and accepts Edgar's offer to help him back to his apartment. At the apartment, Edgar dodges his questions. He seems to seek Lewis' companionship, while Lewis attempts to understand the nature of their encounter.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?165495</url></doc>
